# =============================================================================
# POCKET-ID - Local Development Environment
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to .env.local and edit values as needed.
# For production, secrets come from Locket/Infisical via sidecar.yaml.
#
# Usage: cp .env.example .env.local
#
# NOTE: Pocket-ID manages its own secrets internally via ./data.
# No environment-based secrets are required for the compose.yaml as-is.
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# Pocket-ID (no env vars needed — secrets are stored in ./data volume)
# =============================================================================
# If you later add an external database, uncomment and set:
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://pocketid:password@db:5432/pocketid